# Demo & SEO

Reference: `demo/index.html` — follow existing section patterns.

## HTML accordion markup

Authors omit ARIA — JS adds it. Required classes: `shutters-accordion`, `shutters-item`, `shutters-header`, `shutters-title`, `shutters-icon`, `shutters-content`, `shutters-body`.

## Init pattern

```html
<script type="module">
  import { ShuttersAccordion } from './shutters-core.js';
  new ShuttersAccordion({ container: '.shutters-accordion', ... });
</script>
```

- **Never** load `shutters-core.js` twice (no duplicate script tag + import)
- One instance per independent auto-close group if behavior must differ

## SEO blocks in demo/index.html

- Primary meta, Open Graph, Twitter Card
- JSON-LD: `SoftwareSourceCode` + `FAQPage`
- Update JSON-LD `version` on release

## Build & deploy

- Dev: `npm run dev:demo`
- Production: `npm run build:demo` → `dist-demo/`
- Deploy: push to `main`/`master` triggers `.github/workflows/deploy-demo.yml`

